quran[8{c,v,t}:
6,158,yeh is ke siwa aur kis baat ke munhtazir hain ke un ke paas farishtay ayen ya khud tumhara perwar-digaar aeye ya tumahray perwar-digaar ki kuch nishanain ayen ( magar ) jis roz tumahray perwar-digaar ki kuch nishanain aa jayen gi to jo shakhs pehlay imaan nahi laya hoga is waqt usay imaan lana kuch faida nahi day ga ya apne imaan ( ki haalat ) mein naik amal nahi kiye hon ge ( to gunaaho se tauba karna mufeed nah hoga ae paighambar un se ) keh do ke tum bhi intzaar karo hum bhi intzaar karte hain
6,159,jin logon ne apne deen mein ( bohat se ) raste nikalay aur kayi kayi firqay ho gay un se tum ko kuch kaam nahi un ka kaam khuda ke hawalay phir jo kuch woh karte rahay hain woh un ko ( sab ) betaye ga
6,160,aur jo koi ( khuda ke huzoor ) neki le kar aeye ga is ko waisi das naikian milein gi aur jo buraiee laaye ga usay saza waisay hi miley gi aur un par zulm nahikiya jaye ga
6,161,keh do ke mujhe mere perwar-digaar ne seedha rasta dikha diya hai ( yani deen sahih ) mazhab ibrahim ka jo aik ( khuda ) hi ki taraf ke they aur mushrikon mein se nah they
6,162,( yeh bhi ) keh do ke meri namaz aur meri ibadat aur mera jeena aur mera marna sab khuday-e rab alameen hi ke liye hai
6,163,jis ka koi shareek nahi aur mujh ko isi baat ka hukum mila hai aur mein sab se awwal farmanbardar hon
6,164,kahokiya mein khuda ke siwa aur perwar-digaar talaash karoon aur wohi to har cheez ka maalik hai aur jo koi ( bura ) kaam karta hai to is ka zarrar isi ko hota hai aur koi shakhs kisi ( ke gunah ) ka boojh nahi uthaye ga phir tum sab ko apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lout ka jana hai to jin jin baton mein tum ikhtilaafkiya karte they woh tum ko betaye ga
6,165,aur wohi to hai jis ne zameen mein tum ko apna naib banaya aur aik ke dosray par darjay buland kiye taakay jo kuch is ne tumhe bakhsha hai is mein tumhari azmaish hai be shak tumhara perwar-digaar jald azaab dainay wala hai aur be shak woh bakhsnay wala meharban bhi hai
